Former Mzansi president Thabo Mbeki announced that he was
“ready to assist the new ANC leadership.”He is reported to be working closely with deputy
president Cyril Ramaphosa.Speaking to the SABC in Addis Ababa on Sunday at the
African Union 2018 Summit, Mbeki expressed his support for the president of the
